      <description>&lt;P&gt;I've thought of a couple more since my last post...&lt;/P&gt;&lt;STRONG&gt;&#xD;
&lt;P&gt;&#xD;
&lt;HR&gt;&#xD;
&lt;/P&gt;&#xD;
&lt;P&gt;&lt;EM&gt;All three of these abilities would be on the same timer&lt;/EM&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&#xD;
&lt;P&gt;Defensive Tactics:&lt;/STRONG&gt;&amp;nbsp; 15 -- Extend's the warrior's 5% mitigation bonus (-1 DI) to the rest of the group.&amp;nbsp; Multiple warriors in a group stack. (Duration 5min, resuse 30min, reuse reduction AA reducing to 15min)&lt;BR&gt;&lt;STRONG&gt;Defensive Strategy:&lt;/STRONG&gt;&amp;nbsp; 15 -- Reduces the warrior's DPS by 20%, increases mitigation by 10% for the entire group.&amp;nbsp; (Duration 5min, resuse 30min, reuse reduction AA reducing to 15min)&lt;BR&gt;&lt;STRONG&gt;The Best Defense...:&lt;/STRONG&gt;&amp;nbsp;15 -- Reduces the warriors mitigation by 10% (+2DI) and increases damage by 25%.&amp;nbsp; (Duration 5min, resuse 30min, reuse reduction AA reducing to 15min)&lt;/P&gt;&#xD;
&lt;P&gt;&#xD;
&lt;HR&gt;&#xD;
&lt;/P&gt;&#xD;
&lt;P&gt;&lt;STRONG&gt;Adaptive Doctrine:&lt;/STRONG&gt;&amp;nbsp; 10 -- Allows the warrior to switch between &lt;STRONG&gt;Defensive Tactics, Defensive Strategy, &lt;/STRONG&gt;and&lt;STRONG&gt; The Best Defense...&lt;/STRONG&gt; instantly, as long as the timer is still running.&lt;/P&gt;&#xD;
&lt;P&gt;&lt;STRONG&gt;Bodyguard:&lt;/STRONG&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;5 -- (&lt;EM&gt;Requires Shield Block at level 3) &lt;/EM&gt;Gives the warrior a access to the /Bodyguard command.&amp;nbsp; /Bodyguard NAME sets a character to be "/shield"ed automatically as a passive ability (does not exhaust /shield) and allows hits landed on that character to be shield-blocked, as long as thwe warrior has a shield equipped.&lt;/P&gt;&#xD;
&lt;P&gt;&lt;STRONG&gt;Taking One for the Team:&lt;/STRONG&gt;&amp;nbsp; 15 -- Evacuates all other members of the party, leaving the warrior to "take one for the team".&lt;/P&gt;&#xD;
&lt;P&gt;&lt;STRONG&gt;Noone Saw That, Right?:&lt;/STRONG&gt;&amp;nbsp; 5 -- 100% agro wipe, invisibility, and increased run speed 70% for 1 minute.&amp;nbsp; Only usable when not in group or raid.&amp;nbsp; Reuse 144min.&lt;/P&gt;</description>
