      <title>Re: DoDH AA's you'd like to see</title>
      <link>http://eqforums.station.sony.com/eq/board/message?board.id=warriorbalance&amp;message.id=8259#M8259</link>
      <description>&lt;DIV&gt;&lt;FONT size=2&gt;&#xD;
&lt;P&gt;So here's a partial list that I put together with some input from a few others.&amp;nbsp; Any names presented are purely for reference.&amp;nbsp; Costs and precise details are &lt;STRONG&gt;NOT &lt;/STRONG&gt;required, just a first pass stab at what i felt would be balanced.&amp;nbsp; The real value is in the nature of the AAs and the abilities they enhance and/or add to the class.&lt;/P&gt;&#xD;
&lt;P&gt;Kakgumu&lt;/P&gt;&#xD;
&lt;P&gt;Final Door&lt;/P&gt;&#xD;
&lt;P&gt;70 Warrior of Stromm&lt;/P&gt;&#xD;
&lt;P&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/P&gt;&#xD;
&lt;P&gt;&lt;U&gt;&lt;STRONG&gt;Warrior AAs I'd like to see&lt;/STRONG&gt;&lt;/U&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&#xD;
&lt;P&gt;&lt;STRONG&gt;Perfection of Anger&lt;/STRONG&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&#xD;
&lt;P&gt;Cost: 15&lt;/P&gt;&#xD;
&lt;P&gt;Description: Much like AET, but single target only. Costs&amp;nbsp;500 Endurance and Has a 1:00 recycle time.&lt;/P&gt;&#xD;
&lt;P&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/P&gt;&#xD;
&lt;P&gt;Hastening of Gunnar&lt;/P&gt;&#xD;
&lt;P&gt;Cost: 5/5/5/5/5&lt;/P&gt;&#xD;
&lt;P&gt;Description: Each level reduces the reuse timer on all discs by 5%. Thus, at Level 5 all disc timers are reduced by 25%&lt;/P&gt;&#xD;
&lt;P&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/P&gt;&#xD;
&lt;P&gt;avoidance line increase&lt;/P&gt;&#xD;
&lt;P&gt;Cost: 5/5/5/5/5&lt;/P&gt;&#xD;
&lt;P&gt;Description: Same effect as the PoP/GoD line&lt;/P&gt;&#xD;
&lt;P&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/P&gt;&#xD;
&lt;P&gt;mitigation line increase&lt;/P&gt;&#xD;
&lt;P&gt;Cost: 5/5/5/5/5&lt;/P&gt;&#xD;
&lt;P&gt;Description: Same effect as the PoP/GoD line&lt;/P&gt;&#xD;
&lt;P&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/P&gt;&#xD;
&lt;P&gt;500 HPs in 5 levels (100 HPs / level)&lt;/P&gt;&#xD;
&lt;P&gt;Cost: 5/5/5/5/5&lt;/P&gt;&#xD;
&lt;P&gt;Description: Same effect as the GoD line&lt;/P&gt;&#xD;
&lt;P&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/P&gt;&#xD;
&lt;P&gt;single target stun&lt;/P&gt;&#xD;
&lt;P&gt;Cost: 5/10/15&lt;/P&gt;&#xD;
&lt;P&gt;Description: Hits your target with a limited duration stun. Level 1 = Lvl 65 mobs (and under) for 0.5 secs. Level 2 = Lvl 68 mobs (and under) for 1.0 secs. Level 3 - Lvl 71 mobs (and under) for 1.5 secs.&lt;/P&gt;&lt;B&gt;&#xD;
&lt;P&gt;The Touch of Lord Nikon&lt;/P&gt;&#xD;
&lt;P&gt;&lt;/B&gt;Cost: 3/3/3&lt;/P&gt;&#xD;
&lt;P&gt;Description: Increase distance of the knockback of &amp;lt;name of OoW AA here&amp;gt; by 10' per level.&lt;/P&gt;&lt;B&gt;&#xD;
&lt;P&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/P&gt;&#xD;
&lt;P&gt;Aegis of Lucern&lt;/P&gt;&#xD;
&lt;P&gt;&lt;/B&gt;Cost: 5/5/5/5/5&lt;/P&gt;&#xD;
&lt;P&gt;Description: Each level of this AA increases the AC softcap of the warrior by 10 points.&lt;/P&gt;&lt;B&gt;&#xD;
&lt;P&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/P&gt;&#xD;
&lt;P&gt;Kiwoadi’s Furious Onslaught&lt;/P&gt;&#xD;
&lt;P&gt;&lt;/B&gt;Cost: 2/4/6&lt;/P&gt;&#xD;
&lt;P&gt;Description: Increases the amount of hate generated by Bash and Slam attacks by 50% per level (double for Furious Bash).&lt;/P&gt;&#xD;
&lt;P&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/P&gt;&#xD;
&lt;P&gt;Endurance Regen Increase&lt;/P&gt;&#xD;
&lt;P&gt;Cost: 3/3/3/3/3&lt;/P&gt;&#xD;
&lt;P&gt;Description: Each level of this AA increases the amount of innate Endurance regen by 1 per point.&lt;/P&gt;&#xD;
&lt;P&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/P&gt;&#xD;
&lt;P&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;B&gt;&lt;U&gt;&#xD;
&lt;P&gt;General AAs&lt;/P&gt;&lt;/B&gt;&lt;/U&gt;&#xD;
&lt;P&gt;run speed&lt;/P&gt;&#xD;
&lt;P&gt;Cost: 5/10&lt;/P&gt;&#xD;
&lt;P&gt;Description: Grants a burst of speed that’s equal to 70% run speed for 30 secs per level.&lt;/P&gt;&#xD;
&lt;P&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/P&gt;&#xD;
&lt;P&gt;Forage&lt;/P&gt;&#xD;
&lt;P&gt;Cost: 15&lt;/P&gt;&#xD;
&lt;P&gt;Description: Limited forage ability (skill 50 or 75).&lt;/P&gt;&#xD;
&lt;P&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/P&gt;&#xD;
&lt;P&gt;Self Invis&lt;/P&gt;&#xD;
&lt;P&gt;Cost: 15&lt;/P&gt;&#xD;
&lt;P&gt;Description: Self only invis that has a 1h reuse time and 15:00 duration.&lt;/P&gt;&#xD;
&lt;P&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/P&gt;&#xD;
&lt;P&gt;Critical Care&lt;/P&gt;&#xD;
&lt;P&gt;Cost: 5/5/5&lt;/P&gt;&#xD;
&lt;P&gt;Description: Increase the benefit of each bandage wound by 500/1000/1500 points per bandage.&lt;/P&gt;&lt;B&gt;&lt;U&gt;&lt;/B&gt;&lt;/U&gt;&#xD;
&lt;P&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/P&gt;&#xD;
&lt;P&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;B&gt;&lt;U&gt;&#xD;
&lt;P&gt;Warr Discs&lt;/P&gt;&lt;/B&gt;&lt;/U&gt;&#xD;
&lt;P&gt;Lvl 70 Ancient: improved defensive/stonewall (no detrimental effects, 55% DB reduction + 5% DI reduction). On same timer as other defensive discs. 4:00 duration, 15:00 recycle.&lt;/P&gt;&#xD;
&lt;P&gt;Lvl 70 Ancient: single target, chromatic, 1K DD, uses endurance and has short (&amp;gt;30 secs) recycle time.&lt;/P&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;</description>
