&lt;LI&gt;When a &lt;FONT color=#ff9900&gt;Mob dies &lt;/FONT&gt;AND the Warrior has that mob on his target, the Warrior &lt;FONT color=#ff9900&gt;gains between 400 and 600 endurance &lt;/FONT&gt;(fixes fast killing group running Warrior OOE)&lt;/LI&gt;&#xD;
&lt;LI&gt;&lt;FONT color=#ff9900&gt;Endurance Regen &lt;/FONT&gt;AA that adds &lt;FONT color=#ff9900&gt;60 endurance per tick &lt;/FONT&gt;regen&lt;/LI&gt;&#xD;
