&lt;LI&gt;durabilty (WAR ONLY)&lt;BR&gt;in GoD we got some hp, lets get a &lt;FONT color=#ff9900&gt;raw ac boost&lt;/FONT&gt; instead of a 1.6x mod have it go up to 1.7x raw ac. (help undergeared wars fighting in tougher content)&lt;BR&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/LI&gt;&#xD;
&lt;LI&gt;first strike(3 levels) (WAR ONLY)&lt;BR&gt;1st level &lt;FONT color=#ff9900&gt;first round of combat all main hand attacks land&lt;/FONT&gt;. 2nd level same as first level and all off hand attacks land. 3rd level same as first and second level&amp;nbsp; with the addtion of additional effects(flurry) and main hand weapon procs(1 min reset)&lt;/LI&gt;&#xD;
