&lt;LI&gt;Fearless = 9&lt;BR&gt;-&lt;FONT color=#ff9900&gt;Cannot be feared&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/LI&gt;&#xD;
&lt;LI&gt;Grand Sturdiness = 5, 5, 5, 5, 5 (War ONLY)&lt;BR&gt;-&lt;FONT color=#ff9900&gt;Gain 100 hp each level&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/LI&gt;&#xD;
&lt;LI&gt;Armor Skin = 5, 5, 5, 5, 5 &amp;nbsp;(WAR only)&lt;BR&gt;- &lt;FONT color=#ff9900&gt;Gain 25 ac each level&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/LI&gt;&#xD;
&lt;LI&gt;Procfest:&amp;nbsp; Gives your weapons the ability to &lt;FONT color=#ff9900&gt;proc on every strike for 12 secs &lt;/FONT&gt;&amp;amp; 15 mins reuse. Warrior only.&lt;/LI&gt;&#xD;
&lt;LI&gt;A self-only &lt;FONT color=#ff9900&gt;'Lay hands' for endurance&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/LI&gt;&#xD;
&lt;LI&gt;discipline modifier , endurence&amp;nbsp; cost&amp;nbsp; :&amp;nbsp; 5&amp;nbsp; levels , &lt;FONT color=#ff9900&gt;reduces&amp;nbsp; endurence&amp;nbsp; cost&amp;nbsp; by&amp;nbsp; 10&amp;nbsp; %&amp;nbsp; per&amp;nbsp; level &lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/LI&gt;&#xD;
&lt;LI&gt;discipline modifier , reuse timer&amp;nbsp; reducer&amp;nbsp; : 5&amp;nbsp; levels&lt;FONT color=#ff9900&gt; , reduces&amp;nbsp; reuse time on&amp;nbsp; all&amp;nbsp; disciplines&lt;/FONT&gt;&amp;nbsp; by&amp;nbsp; 10&amp;nbsp; %&amp;nbsp; per&amp;nbsp; level &lt;/LI&gt;&#xD;
&lt;LI&gt;physical damage &lt;FONT color=#ff9900&gt;voidence&amp;nbsp; and&amp;nbsp; midigation aa's&amp;nbsp; above&amp;nbsp; what&amp;nbsp; other&amp;nbsp; classes&amp;nbsp; get&amp;nbsp; &lt;/FONT&gt;,&amp;nbsp; as&amp;nbsp; in&amp;nbsp; ,&amp;nbsp; if&amp;nbsp; other&amp;nbsp; classes&amp;nbsp; get 5&amp;nbsp; levels&amp;nbsp; ,&amp;nbsp; then&amp;nbsp; warrior&amp;nbsp; should get&amp;nbsp; an&amp;nbsp; additional&amp;nbsp; 5&amp;nbsp; levels . &lt;/LI&gt;&#xD;
&lt;LI&gt;&lt;FONT color=#ff9900&gt;spell&amp;nbsp; mitigation&amp;nbsp; similar to&amp;nbsp; spell&amp;nbsp; shielding&amp;nbsp; &lt;/FONT&gt;, 5&amp;nbsp; levels&amp;nbsp; ,&amp;nbsp; 10 %&amp;nbsp; mitigation&amp;nbsp; and 10&amp;nbsp; %&amp;nbsp; dot timer reduction per&amp;nbsp; level &lt;/LI&gt;&#xD;
&lt;LI&gt;&lt;FONT color=#ff9900&gt;ambidexterity&amp;nbsp; upgrade , hits&amp;nbsp; with&amp;nbsp; both&amp;nbsp; weaps&amp;nbsp; as&amp;nbsp; main&amp;nbsp; hand &lt;/FONT&gt;( meaning&amp;nbsp; strength&amp;nbsp; bonus on&amp;nbsp; both ) &lt;/LI&gt;&#xD;
&lt;LI&gt;spell&amp;nbsp; reflection&amp;nbsp; , 10&amp;nbsp; levels , &lt;FONT color=#ff9900&gt;reflects&amp;nbsp; spell&amp;nbsp; effects&amp;nbsp; by&amp;nbsp; 3 %&amp;nbsp; per level&amp;nbsp;&lt;/FONT&gt; ,stacks prior&amp;nbsp; to&amp;nbsp; spell&amp;nbsp; mitigation&amp;nbsp; aa &lt;/LI&gt;&#xD;
&lt;LI&gt;&lt;FONT color=#ff9900&gt;Area /Shielding&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;BR&gt;ie; instead of /shielding target, you would push a Hotbutton and &lt;FONT color=#ff9900&gt;Shield whomever your target is attacking&lt;/FONT&gt;.&lt;/LI&gt;&#xD;
&lt;LI&gt;Celestial Anchor:&amp;nbsp; Once activated the &lt;FONT color=#ff9900&gt;target has less of a chance to gate successfully&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;BR&gt;Level 1 is 10% less likely to gate successfully&lt;BR&gt;Level 2 is 20% less likely to gate successfully&lt;BR&gt;Level 3 is 50% less likely to gate successfully&lt;/LI&gt;&#xD;
&lt;LI&gt;critical tuants.... a chance for &lt;FONT color=#ff9900&gt;taunts to cause critical aggro &lt;/FONT&gt;also allow this to attach to al the ae taunts.&lt;/LI&gt;&#xD;
&lt;LI&gt;counter attack.. a &lt;FONT color=#ff9900&gt;chance to counter attack after taking a hit&lt;/FONT&gt; 5 levels 5-25% (&lt;FONT color=#ff9900&gt;not a riposte &lt;/FONT&gt;because you do take the damage)&lt;/LI&gt;&#xD;
&lt;LI&gt;Alarming Incite-&lt;FONT color=#ff9900&gt; A stun effect added to incite line &lt;/FONT&gt;to the initial landing, additional ranks in the AA increase the likelihood of a stun chance per tick. The stun is representated by a momentary panic state from the loud noise caused by the incite.&lt;/LI&gt;&#xD;
&lt;LI&gt;Impale- The ability to impale any weapon into the hide of a creature, gain the &lt;FONT color=#ff9900&gt;ability to pick up and move or otherwise drag that mob &lt;/FONT&gt;for a limited time before the mob becomes freed of your weapon's grasp.&lt;/LI&gt;&#xD;
&lt;LI&gt;Offhand parry: &lt;FONT color=#ff9900&gt;WAR Only Shield Block for offhand weapons&lt;/FONT&gt;.&lt;/LI&gt;&#xD;
&lt;LI&gt;Blaze of Glory: &lt;FONT color=#ff9900&gt;For ten seconds, the warrior is immune to all damage.&amp;nbsp; All attacks will hit and will do critical damage&lt;/FONT&gt;.&amp;nbsp; At the end of the ten seconds, &lt;FONT color=#ff9900&gt;the warrior dies, irregardless of how many hit points &lt;/FONT&gt;or what spells they had on them prior.&amp;nbsp; Recharge of 3 hours.&amp;nbsp; Cost of 5 points - Designed to be used when the warrior is going to die anyway; at least now he can die in style.&lt;/LI&gt;&#xD;
&lt;LI&gt;Walking Arsenal (Level 1-3): The warrior can have more weapons available for their rapid use.&amp;nbsp; 5 points a level.&amp;nbsp; - Each level gives the warrior &lt;FONT color=#ff9900&gt;one more slot on their bandolier &lt;/FONT&gt;to save a weapon configuration.&amp;nbsp; Four slots is not enough for my warrior to store all the weapon configurations he needs.&amp;nbsp; There are his aggro weapons, his snare weapon (silken whip of ensnaring), his slow weapon (truncheon of doom), his summon bandages weapons (embalmer's skinning knife), etc.&lt;/LI&gt;&#xD;
&lt;LI&gt;Cazic's Pressence (9) - &lt;FONT color=#ff9900&gt;Green cons will no longer attack you&lt;/FONT&gt;. &lt;/LI&gt;&#xD;
&lt;LI&gt;Sayrn's Grip (9) - &lt;FONT color=#ff9900&gt;Increases Stuns done by kick &lt;/FONT&gt;for 1 second. &lt;/LI&gt;&#xD;
&lt;LI&gt;Innorruuk's Laughter (9) - &lt;FONT color=#ff9900&gt;Increase Hate done by combat abilities &lt;/FONT&gt;by 5%. &lt;/LI&gt;&#xD;
&lt;LI&gt;Raex's Bloodthirst (12) - The ability to &lt;FONT color=#ff9900&gt;regain 300 Endurance after dealing a final blow &lt;/FONT&gt;to an opponent. &lt;/LI&gt;&#xD;
&lt;LI&gt;War Veteran's Counter (3,3,3) - &lt;FONT color=#ff9900&gt;Heightened chance to critical on a riposte &lt;/FONT&gt;by 15, 25, 35% &lt;/LI&gt;&#xD;
&lt;LI&gt;Strategy of Vallon (9) - &lt;FONT color=#ff9900&gt;Higher chance of parrying &lt;/FONT&gt;by 5% &lt;/LI&gt;&#xD;
&lt;LI&gt;Tactics of Tallon (9) - &lt;FONT color=#ff9900&gt;Higher chance of dodging &lt;/FONT&gt;by 5% &lt;/LI&gt;&#xD;
&lt;LI&gt;Blitz of Rallos (9) - &lt;FONT color=#ff9900&gt;Higher chance of riposting &lt;/FONT&gt;by 5% &lt;/LI&gt;&#xD;
&lt;LI&gt;Blood, Toil, Sweat, and Tears 5/5/5 -- Allows the warrior to&lt;FONT color=#ff9900&gt; continue to use endurance abilities when the endurance bar is depleted&lt;/FONT&gt;... At the cost of HPs.&amp;nbsp; First level is 3*END cost in HP, Second level is 2.5*END cost, Third level is 2*END cost.&lt;/LI&gt;&#xD;
&lt;LI&gt;Fury of the Depths 3/6/9 -- &lt;FONT color=#ff9900&gt;Increase hate generated by Incite line abilities &lt;/FONT&gt;by 10/25/50%&lt;/LI&gt;&#xD;
&lt;LI&gt;single target stun Cost: 5/10/15&lt;BR&gt;&amp;nbsp;Description: Hits &lt;FONT color=#ff9900&gt;your target with a limited duration stun&lt;/FONT&gt;. Level 1 = Lvl 65 mobs (and under) for 0.5 secs. Level 2 = Lvl 68 mobs (and under) for 1.0 secs. Level 3 - &lt;FONT color=#ff9900&gt;Lvl 71 mobs (and under&lt;/FONT&gt;) for 1.5 secs.&lt;/LI&gt;&#xD;
&lt;LI&gt;Kiwoadi’s Furious Onslaught Cost: 2/4/6 Description: &lt;FONT color=#ff9900&gt;Increases the amount of hate generated by Bash and Slam attacks by 500% per level &lt;/FONT&gt;(double for Furious Bash).&amp;nbsp; 1500 % (level 3) would increase the 23 hate to a reasonable 345 points of hate.&amp;nbsp; Stacks with FB, so FB7 would be 586 hate per bash.&amp;nbsp; (War ONLY)&lt;/LI&gt;&#xD;
&lt;LI&gt;Lvl 70 Ancient: &lt;FONT color=#ff9900&gt;improved defensive/stonewall &lt;/FONT&gt;(no detrimental effects, &lt;FONT color=#ff9900&gt;55% DB reduction + 5% DI reduction&lt;/FONT&gt;). On same timer as other defensive discs. 4:00 duration, 15:00 recycle.&lt;/LI&gt;&lt;/UL&gt;&#xD;
